05:24.341 --> 05:25.914
Wait, you want
to talk to who?

05:27.781 --> 05:30.104
You want to tell
him you love him?

05:31.266 --> 05:35.188
Well, I don't know. You guys didn't
really leave on the best of terms.

05:36.421 --> 05:37.266
