I'll never forget. It was
the hottest day of summer,

05:57.973 --> 06:01.190
and Hyde and Kelso dug a hole
then covered it with leaves.

06:02.893 --> 06:06.533
And they said, "Hey, Fez, want
to see a pile of dead leaves?"

06:10.387 --> 06:12.747
So naturally, I ran over.

06:14.000 --> 06:14.748
What happened?

06:15.073 --> 06:16.376
I fell in,

06:16.881 --> 06:18.290
and I couldn't get out.

06:18.584 --> 06:20.434
And the sun was
beating down.

06:20.904 --> 06:22.841
So hot. So hot.

06:25.742 --> 06:27.949
Finally, Eric came over.

06:27.994 --> 06:30.495
And you know what that
magnificent boy did?

06:32.467 --> 06:35.004
