the waterworks!

07:01.522 --> 07:03.682
- Hey, Hyde, man.
- Hey, man.

07:04.516 --> 07:08.297
Listen, I want some tunes, so
I need to find a record store.

07:15.888 --> 07:17.778
Leo, you're in
