gonna forget this conversation when it's over.

08:01.620 --> 08:04.166
Hey, that's not true, man.

08:04.400 --> 08:06.432
Hey, guess what I found out.

08:06.455 --> 08:07.406
What, Leo?

08:07.665 --> 08:09.858
Loud girl's in Chicago.

08:15.402 --> 08:18.642
Oh, crap. It's almost time
for me to go get my shots.

08:18.842 --> 08:21.120
