job and a haircut!

11:07.036 --> 11:08.058
And you...

11:08.410 --> 11:13.694
wipe that stupid smirk off
your dopey, dope-fiend face!

11:15.180 --> 11:16.578
Do you know what
drugs do to you?

11:17.681 --> 11:22.824
They shrink your brain until one day you wake
up, and you think you're superman and you can fly,

11:22.848 --> 11:26.916
and then you wind up jumping
off the roof in your underpants.

11:30.309 --> 11:32.834
Oh, this idiot doesn't
need drugs for that.

11:32.869 --> 11:34.783
He does that every saturday.

11:38.838 --> 11:42.384
Well, this is the worst thing
that you have ever done!

11:42.699 --> 11:45.129
Eric, I am gonna make you...

11:47.325 --> 11:48.699
I am going to...

11:50.566 --> 11:53.622
Well, I can't think of anything
worse than sending you to Africa.

11:54.373 --> 11:55.782
You're going to Africa!

11:59.643 --> 12:00.641
Hey, Leo.

12:02.566 --> 12:03.423
So

12:03.752 --> 12:07.192
I decided that tomorrow after I say
