15:08.130 --> 15:09.797
I'm your father, so...

15:12.263 --> 15:13.202
here.

15:15.203 --> 15:17.246
That's your pocket
knife from Korea.

15:18.279 --> 15:23.453
You said if I ever touched that, I'd meet the
same fate as hundreds of other godless commies.

15:25.472 --> 15:26.459
Well,

15:27.797 --> 15:30.192
