it to Africa.

15:32.059 --> 15:32.936
Really?

15:35.894 --> 15:38.125
Wow, dad, that means a lot.

15:38.983 --> 15:41.084
And, son, I want
you to know that

15:41.530 --> 15:44.547
I'm gonna miss you, and I
love you, and have a good trip.

15:46.203 --> 15:48.152
Wait a second. What
did you just say?

15:49.829 --> 15:51.332
I said have a good trip.

15:52.353 --> 15:54.619
No, before that.

15:55.935 --> 15:57.038
