then we're gonna have our whole lives to spend together.

17:31.065 --> 17:32.697
Listen to me, Donna.

17:34.588 --> 17:36.431
I love you so much.

17:37.464 --> 17:39.423
You know, you're
my best friend.

17:39.974 --> 17:40.878
And I...

17:44.730 --> 17:45.763
